<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 10:08:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>孟加拉国首席顾问尤努斯：复兴南盟精神可以解决许多地区问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/revival-of-saarc-spirit-can-solve-many-regional-problems-bangladeshs-chief-adviser-yunus/articleshow/113122204.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113122204.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;孟加拉国临时政府首脑穆罕默德·尤努斯主张重振南盟以解决地区问题。他打算在联合国大会期间会见印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪，并计划聚集南盟领导人合影留念。尤努斯还寻求印度帮助解决影响孟加拉国的罗兴亚人危机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:18:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/revival-of-saarc-spirit-can-solve-many-regional-problems-bangladeshs-chief-adviser-yunus/articleshow/113122204.cms</guid></item><item><title>新泽西州发生争执后，“精神病患者”放火烧毁女友父母的家</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/psychopath-sets-girlfriends-parents-home-on-fire-after-dispute-in-new-jersey/articleshow/113119932.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113119932.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在南不伦瑞克，50 岁的伦纳德·琼斯据称在与女友发生争执后放火烧毁了女友的父母的家。事件发生在凌晨3点左右，警方立即做出反应。当大火吞没房屋时，所有四名居民都设法安全逃生。琼斯随后被捕并被指控犯有严重纵火罪和家庭暴力罪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:04:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/psychopath-sets-girlfriends-parents-home-on-fire-after-dispute-in-new-jersey/articleshow/113119932.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国宣布向乌克兰提供额外援助，泽伦斯基在德国会见最高军事领导人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/zelenskyy-meets-top-military-leaders-in-germany-as-the-us-announces-additional-aid-to-ukraine/articleshow/113121468.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113121468.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰总统泽连斯基在德国会见了美国军方领导人和 50 多个伙伴国家，以推动更多武器支持。美国宣布向乌克兰追加2.5亿美元安全援助。随着泽连斯基寻求远程打击能力，讨论的重点是防空、火炮供应和加强乌克兰的国防工业基础。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:53:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/zelenskyy-meets-top-military-leaders-in-germany-as-the-us-announces-additional-aid-to-ukraine/articleshow/113121468.cms</guid></item><item><title>“学校枪击……我很害怕”：佐治亚州阿巴拉奇袭击事件期间，家长和学生分享了令人心碎的信息</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/school-shooting-im-scared-parents-and-students-share-heart-wrenching-messages-during-apalachee-high-attack-in-georgia/articleshow/113121133.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113121133.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;佐治亚州温德市的阿巴拉奇高中发生悲惨枪击事件，造成四人死亡、九人受伤。封锁期间，学生们给父母发了绝望的短信。被指控的枪手是一名 14 岁学生，目前面临多项指控。受害者包括两名教师和两名学生。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/school-shooting-im-scared-parents-and-students-share-heart-wrenching-messages-during-apalachee-high-attack-in-georgia/articleshow/113121133.cms</guid></item><item><title>“想像其他孩子一样玩耍”：轮滑运动员加沙女孩在以色列空袭中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/wanted-to-play-like-other-children-roller-skater-gaza-girls-life-cut-short-in-israeli-airstrike/articleshow/113120641.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113120641.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;胡萨姆·萨拉赫·阿布·阿吉瓦 (Hussam Salah Abu Ajwa) 让他的女儿塔拉 (Tala) 在加沙城外面玩耍，但不久后发生爆炸，导致她身亡。冲突蹂躏了该地区，学校遭到破坏，许多家庭流离失所。近东救济工程处警告说，持续的暴力可能会导致一代人因长期冲突而充满怨恨和极端主义。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/wanted-to-play-like-other-children-roller-skater-gaza-girls-life-cut-short-in-israeli-airstrike/articleshow/113120641.cms</guid></item><item><title>小泉进次郎宣布若当选日本新领导人将提前选举</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/shinjiro-koizumi-announces-plan-for-early-election-if-elected-as-japans-new-leader/articleshow/113119405.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113119405.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前环境大臣、日本首相职位的主要竞争者小泉进次郎宣布，如果在即将举行的执政党领导人竞选中获胜，计划提前举行选举。他打算维持现有的经济政策，同时增强经济实力。 9月27日的自民党选举将决定下一任首相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/shinjiro-koizumi-announces-plan-for-early-election-if-elected-as-japans-new-leader/articleshow/113119405.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴伦·特朗普：唐纳德在美国总统选举中争取 Z 世代选票的“秘密武器”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/barron-trump-donalds-secret-weapon-in-fight-for-gen-z-votes-in-us-presidential-elections/articleshow/113119110.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113119110.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 正在利用他的儿子巴伦 (Barron) 为即将到来的 2024 年大选吸引 Z 世代选民。巴伦的角色包括与数字平台和有影响力的人接触，增强特朗普与年轻观众的联系。根据 SurveyUSA 的一项民意调查，特朗普在 18-34 岁选民中领先于卡马拉·哈里斯。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:17:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/barron-trump-donalds-secret-weapon-in-fight-for-gen-z-votes-in-us-presidential-elections/articleshow/113119110.cms</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉司机被发现在自动驾驶仪上睡着并携带价值 10 万美元的非法毒品被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tesla-driver-arrested-after-being-found-asleep-on-autopilot-with-100k-in-illegal-drugs/articleshow/113113563.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113113563.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;迈克尔·古德曼 (Michael Goodman) 在北卡罗来纳州威尔逊米尔斯 (Wilson&amp;#39;s Mills) 被捕，原因是在他的特斯拉自动驾驶仪方向盘后面睡着了。当局在车内发现了价值超过10万美元的非法毒品。他面临多项重罪指控，例如贩毒和鲁莽驾驶。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tesla-driver-arrested-after-being-found-asleep-on-autopilot-with-100k-in-illegal-drugs/articleshow/113113563.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统对战舰上的水兵说：“我支持你们”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ive-got-your-backs-taiwan-president-tells-sailors-on-combat-ready-warship/articleshow/113119076.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113119076.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾总统赖清德参观了台湾海峡澎湖群岛基地的一艘战备军舰，在与北京的紧张关系加剧之际表达了对水兵的支持。他强调海军内部的团结，致力于提高军事能力，强调他们在维护台湾安全方面的作用。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ive-got-your-backs-taiwan-president-tells-sailors-on-combat-ready-warship/articleshow/113119076.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国对超强台风“八木”保持警惕：关于2024年世界第二强风暴您需要了解的一切</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-on-alert-for-super-typhoon-yagi-all-you-need-to-know-about-the-worlds-second-strongest-storm-of-2024/articleshow/113115981.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113115981.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国正在为周五下午超强台风“八木”登陆做准备，该台风将给广东和海南带来强风、暴雨和沿海洪水的影响。超过41万居民已被疏散。深圳和海南官员对潜在的灾难性损害发出警告，主张在交通服务暂停的情况下进行大规模疏散和采取紧急措施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-on-alert-for-super-typhoon-yagi-all-you-need-to-know-about-the-worlds-second-strongest-storm-of-2024/articleshow/113115981.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国专家：必须向苏丹部署“公正的部队”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/impartial-force-must-be-deployed-to-sudan-un-experts/articleshow/113117730.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113117730.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国专家敦促建立一支独立部队来保护因苏丹国家军队与准军事部队之间持续冲突而流离失所的数百万平民。实况调查团发现了严重侵犯人权的行为，包括对平民目标的空袭和性暴力，这些行为可能构成战争罪。需要立即采取行动保护受影响人群。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:06:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/impartial-force-must-be-deployed-to-sudan-un-experts/articleshow/113117730.cms</guid></item><item><title>新民主党领袖贾格米特·辛格结束自由主义协议，引用加拿大人的重大胜利：“我们取得了很多成就”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ndp-leader-jagmeet-singh-ends-liberal-deal-cites-major-wins-for-canadians-we-accomplished-a-lot/articleshow/113116972.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113116972.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新民主党领袖贾格米特·辛格 (Jagmeet Singh) 宣布终止与自由党政府的供应和信心协议，理由是牙科护理和国家药物保健方面取得的进展等重大成就。辛格批评特鲁多总理过度受企业利益影响。由于新民主党的决定将根据投票结果做出，因此举行选举的可能性似乎更大。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ndp-leader-jagmeet-singh-ends-liberal-deal-cites-major-wins-for-canadians-we-accomplished-a-lot/articleshow/113116972.cms</guid></item><item><title>帕维尔·杜罗夫在法国被捕后的首次声明：“Telegram 并不完美……”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/pavel-durovs-first-statement-after-arrest-in-france-telegram-is-not-perfect-/articleshow/113111697.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113111697.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; Telegram 联合创始人帕维尔·杜罗夫 (Pavel Durov) 在法国被捕后，为自己的平台辩护，反对其纵容犯罪活动的指控。他承认 Telegram 的缺陷，但强调正在努力删除有害内容并增强系统。他批评法国当局的个人责任，并向用户保证即将进行改进，以有效解决滥用问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 06:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/pavel-durovs-first-statement-after-arrest-in-france-telegram-is-not-perfect-/articleshow/113111697.cms</guid></item><item><title>93 天后，美国宇航局陷入困境的星际客机为无人驾驶返回地球做好了准备</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/after-93-days-nasas-troubled-starliner-setting-stage-for-unpiloted-return-to-earth/articleshow/113112726.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113112726.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波音公司的 Starliner 太空舱定于 9 月 6 日从国际空间站脱离，六小时后降落在新墨西哥州。宇航员布奇·威尔莫尔 (Butch Wilmore) 和苏尼塔·威廉姆斯 (Sunita Williams) 将在国际空间站停留到二月份，并乘坐 SpaceX Crew Dragon 渡轮返回。这次任务遇到了氦气泄漏和推进器问题，但目标是成功着陆。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 04:26:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/after-93-days-nasas-troubled-starliner-setting-stage-for-unpiloted-return-to-earth/articleshow/113112726.cms</guid></item><item><title>万斯：“约翰·麦凯恩不会在边境危机上与哈里斯站在一起”，特朗普的竞选伙伴回应已故参议员的儿子支持卡马拉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/vance-john-mccain-wouldnt-stand-with-harris-on-border-crisis-trumps-running-mate-responds-to-late-senators-son-endorsing-kamala/articleshow/113111760.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113111760.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;共和党副总统候选人JD·万斯声称，已故参议员约翰·麦凯恩如果活着亲眼目睹当前南部边境局势，也不会支持副总统卡马拉·哈里斯。他的言论是在麦凯恩的儿子支持哈里斯并注册为民主党人之后发表的。万斯强调，选民的意见优先于家庭的支持。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 05:40:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/vance-john-mccain-wouldnt-stand-with-harris-on-border-crisis-trumps-running-mate-responds-to-late-senators-son-endorsing-kamala/articleshow/113111760.cms</guid></item><item><title>Rich Homie Quan 是谁？说唱歌手被发现口吐白沫，34岁被宣布死亡：发生了什么事？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-was-rich-homie-quan-rap-star-found-foaming-at-mouth-pronounced-dead-at-34-what-happened/articleshow/113111781.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113111781.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;亚特兰大说唱歌手 Rich Homie Quan，原名 Dequantes Devontay Lamar，被发现死亡，享年 34 岁。死因尚未确定，预计将进行尸检。他以《Type of Way》和《Flex》等热门歌曲而闻名，他的去世让歌迷和音乐界感到震惊。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 05:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-was-rich-homie-quan-rap-star-found-foaming-at-mouth-pronounced-dead-at-34-what-happened/articleshow/113111781.cms</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 致命的“镀铬”挑战趋势：Z 世代和 Alpha 世代之间日益严重的危机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tiktoks-deadly-chroming-challenge-trend-growing-crisis-among-gen-z-and-gen-alpha/articleshow/113111868.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113111868.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; TikTok 上一种名为“铬化”的新趋势，即吸入气雾罐中的有毒烟雾以获得暂时的快感，已导致数名青少年死亡。尽管 TikTok 努力删除有害内容，但这种趋势仍在继续。家庭和当局敦促采取更严格的社交媒体监管，并提高家长的警惕性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 05:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tiktoks-deadly-chroming-challenge-trend-growing-crisis-among-gen-z-and-gen-alpha/articleshow/113111868.cms</guid></item><item><title>艾伦·利希特曼是谁，“美国总统民调预测的诺查丹玛斯”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-is-allan-lichtman-the-nostradamus-of-us-presidential-poll-predictions/articleshow/113111708.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113111708.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;历史学家艾伦·利希特曼 (Allan Lichtman) 以精确的总统选举预测而闻名，他采用了一种名为“白宫钥匙”的模型。他根据对 13 个政治因素的分析，预测卡马拉·哈里斯将在 2024 年大选中击败唐纳德·特朗普。利奇曼的方法强调历史模式而不是民意调查数据或竞选策略。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 04:21:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-is-allan-lichtman-the-nostradamus-of-us-presidential-poll-predictions/articleshow/113111708.cms</guid></item><item><title>佐治亚州校园枪击案嫌疑人之父因二级谋杀罪被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/father-of-georgia-school-shooting-suspect-arrested-on-charges-including-second-degree-murder/articleshow/113111211.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113111211.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;佐治亚州一名父亲因 14 岁儿子涉嫌在一所高中枪杀四人而被捕。这位父亲因允许儿子拥有武器而面临二级谋杀和过失杀人罪等指控。此案突显了在校园枪击事件中追究家长责任的趋势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 03:28:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/father-of-georgia-school-shooting-suspect-arrested-on-charges-including-second-degree-murder/articleshow/113111211.cms</guid></item><item><title>教宗在印度尼西亚举行最后弥撒后前往巴布亚新几内亚，现场挤满了十万名群众</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pope-heads-to-papua-new-guinea-after-final-mass-in-indonesia-before-an-overflow-crowd-of-100000/articleshow/113111215.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113111215.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;教宗方济各以十万人参加的弥撒结束了对印度尼西亚的访问，敦促他们建设和平与希望。他现在前往巴布亚新几内亚会见天主教传教士并解决社会正义问题。在印度尼西亚，他专注于促进与穆斯林社区的宗教间对话。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 03:28:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pope-heads-to-papua-new-guinea-after-final-mass-in-indonesia-before-an-overflow-crowd-of-100000/articleshow/113111215.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>